description:
Drudesk is a Drupal website support service whose main mission is to provide the smooth work of Drupal websites. 
The company’s most popular services include:
- Drupal core updates;
- Drupal module updates;
- Drupal migration;
- website development from scratch;
- server monitoring;
- fixing the website after hackers’ attacks;
- bug fixes;
- web design
- UX/UI design
- website audit
- website optimization
- speed optimization
- DevOps
- SEO audit
Learn more at drudesk.com
Drudesk was founded in April, 2015 as a small team inside the famous InternetDevels Drupal development company, but has grown into a full-fledged company with almost 70 employees and customers from across the globe. 
The company works side-by-side with InternetDevels, is an active member of the Drupal community, makes commits to drupal.org, and participates in big Drupal events.
 
